{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":564,"text":"So just by a show of hands, how many of you all have a robot at home?"},{"time":5650,"text":"Not very many of you."},{"time":7590,"text":"Okay. And actually of those hands,"},{"time":9586,"text":"if you don't include Roomba how many of you have a robot at home?"},{"time":12619,"text":"So a couple."},{"time":14076,"text":"That's okay."},{"time":14979,"text":"That's the problem that we're trying to solve at Romotive --"},{"time":17454,"text":"that I and the other 20 nerds at Romotive are obsessed with solving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20325,"text":"So we really want to build a robot that anyone can use,"},{"time":24327,"text":"whether you're eight or 80."},{"time":26579,"text":"And as it turns out, that's a really hard problem,"},{"time":29303,"text":"because you have to build a small, portable robot"},{"time":32036,"text":"that's not only really affordable,"},{"time":34412,"text":"but it has to be something"},{"time":35953,"text":"that people actually want to take home and have around their kids."},{"time":39940,"text":"This robot can't be creepy or uncanny."},{"time":43237,"text":"He should be friendly and cute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45448,"text":"So meet Romo."},{"time":48359,"text":"Romo's a robot that uses a device you already know and love --"},{"time":52216,"text":"your iPhone -- as his brain."},{"time":55065,"text":"And by leveraging the power of the iPhone's processor,"},{"time":59176,"text":"we can create a robot that is wi-fi enabled"},{"time":63627,"text":"and computer vision-capable for 150 bucks,"},{"time":67311,"text":"which is about one percent of what these kinds of robots have cost in the past."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72243,"text":"When Romo wakes up, he's in creature mode."},{"time":75860,"text":"So he's actually using the video camera on the device to follow my face."},{"time":80977,"text":"If I duck down, he'll follow me."},{"time":82476,"text":"He's wary, so he'll keep his eyes on me."},{"time":84802,"text":"If I come over here, he'll turn to follow me."},{"time":88078,"text":"If I come over here -- (Laughs)"},{"time":92279,"text":"He's smart."},{"time":93662,"text":"And if I get too close to him,"},{"time":95876,"text":"he gets scared just like any other creature."},{"time":99009,"text":"So in a lot of ways, Romo is like a pet that has a mind of his own."},{"time":102459,"text":"Thanks, little guy."},{"time":104352,"text":"(Sneezing sound)"},{"time":105734,"text":"Bless you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107825,"text":"And if I want to explore the world -- uh-oh, Romo's tired --"},{"time":112443,"text":"if I want to explore the world with Romo,"},{"time":114458,"text":"I can actually connect him from any other iOS device."},{"time":117392,"text":"So here's the iPad."},{"time":118952,"text":"And Romo will actually stream video to this device."},{"time":121693,"text":"So I can see everything that Romo sees,"},{"time":123326,"text":"and I get a robot's-eye-view of the world."},{"time":125358,"text":"Now this is a free app on the App Store,"},{"time":126794,"text":"so if any of you guys had this app on your phones,"},{"time":128516,"text":"we could literally right now share control of the robot and play games together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132243,"text":"So I'll show you really quickly,"},{"time":133925,"text":"Romo actually -- he's streaming video,"},{"time":135771,"text":"so you can see me and the entire TED audience."},{"time":137961,"text":"If I get in front of Romo here."},{"time":139493,"text":"And if I want to control him, I can just drive."},{"time":142534,"text":"So I can drive him around,"},{"time":146986,"text":"and I can take pictures of you."},{"time":148912,"text":"I've always wanted a picture of a 1,500-person TED audience."},{"time":151317,"text":"So I'll snap a picture."},{"time":152819,"text":"And in the same way that you scroll through content on an iPad,"},{"time":155379,"text":"I can actually adjust the angle of the camera on the device."},{"time":158969,"text":"So there are all of you through Romo's eyes."},{"time":163700,"text":"And finally, because Romo is an extension of me,"},{"time":166786,"text":"I can express myself through his emotions."},{"time":168804,"text":"So I can go in and I can say let's make Romo excited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174070,"text":"But the most important thing about Romo"},{"time":175453,"text":"is that we wanted to create something that was literally completely intuitive."},{"time":180543,"text":"You do not have to teach someone how to drive Romo."},{"time":183127,"text":"In fact, who would like to drive a robot?"},{"time":186095,"text":"Okay. Awesome."},{"time":188627,"text":"Here you go."},{"time":190261,"text":"Thank you, Scott."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193115,"text":"And even cooler, you actually don't have to be"},{"time":195869,"text":"in the same geographic location as the robot to control him."},{"time":200276,"text":"So he actually streams two-way audio and video"},{"time":203561,"text":"between any two smart devices."},{"time":205202,"text":"So you can log in through the browser,"},{"time":207010,"text":"and it's kind of like Skype on wheels."},{"time":208494,"text":"So we were talking before about telepresence,"},{"time":210228,"text":"and this is a really cool example."},{"time":211660,"text":"You can imagine an eight-year-old girl, for example, who has an iPhone,"},{"time":215977,"text":"and her mom buys her a robot."},{"time":217494,"text":"That girl can take her iPhone, put it on the robot,"},{"time":220395,"text":"send an email to Grandma, who lives on the other side of the country."},{"time":223024,"text":"Grandma can log into that robot and play hide-and-go-seek with her granddaughter"},{"time":226378,"text":"for fifteen minutes every single night,"},{"time":228702,"text":"when otherwise she might only be able to get to see her granddaughter once or twice a year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232013,"text":"Thanks, Scott."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233545,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239229,"text":"So those are a couple of the really cool things that Romo can do today."},{"time":242576,"text":"But I just want to finish by talking about something that we're working on in the future."},{"time":246536,"text":"This is actually something that one of our engineers, Dom, built in a weekend."},{"time":250061,"text":"It's built on top of a Google open framework called Blockly."},{"time":253429,"text":"This allows you to drag and drop these blocks of semantic code"},{"time":257525,"text":"and create any behavior for this robot you want."},{"time":259704,"text":"You do not have to know how to code to create a behavior for Romo."},{"time":262485,"text":"And you can actually simulate that behavior in the browser,"},{"time":265345,"text":"which is what you see Romo doing on the left."},{"time":267315,"text":"And then if you have something you like,"},{"time":268666,"text":"you can download it onto your robot and execute it in real life,"},{"time":271761,"text":"run the program in real life."},{"time":273245,"text":"And then if you have something you're proud of,"},{"time":274952,"text":"you can share it with every other person who owns a robot in the world."},{"time":278493,"text":"So all of these wi-fiâ€“enabled robots actually learn from each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281619,"text":"The reason we're so focused on building robots that everyone can train"},{"time":285929,"text":"is that we think the most compelling use cases in personal robotics are personal."},{"time":290518,"text":"They change from person to person."},{"time":293124,"text":"So we think that if you're going to have a robot in your home,"},{"time":295540,"text":"that robot ought to be a manifestation of your own imagination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299691,"text":"So I wish that I could tell you what the future of personal robotics looks like."},{"time":303543,"text":"To be honest, I have no idea."},{"time":306027,"text":"But what we do know is that it isn't 10 years or 10 billion dollars"},{"time":311130,"text":"or a large humanoid robot away."},{"time":314457,"text":"The future of personal robotics is happening today,"},{"time":317458,"text":"and it's going to depend on small, agile robots like Romo"},{"time":321041,"text":"and the creativity of people like yourselves."},{"time":324036,"text":"So we can't wait to get you all robots,"},{"time":326218,"text":"and we can't wait to see what you build."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327946,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329128,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}